---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Readerly — Learn words in context"
  description="Readerly turns short stories into vocabulary you can practice. Read, tap words, and review with spaced repetition."
>
  <header class="border-b border-emerald-100 bg-white">
    <nav class="container flex items-center justify-between py-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">
        <span class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink text-white">
          R
        </span>
        Readerly
      </div>
      <a
        class="rounded-full border border-emerald-200 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-ink transition hover:border-emerald-400"
        href="https://app.readerly.ai"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        Open Readerly
      </a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="container grid gap-12 pb-20 pt-16 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">
          Read-first vocabulary learning
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-ink sm:text-5xl">
          Learn words in context, remember them for real.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted">
          Readerly turns short stories into vocabulary you can practice. Read, tap
          words, and review with spaced repetition that fits your pace.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-soft transition hover:bg-emerald-600"
            href="https://app.readerly.ai"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >
            Open Readerly
          </a>
          <a
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-emerald-200 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink transition hover:border-emerald-400"
            href="#how-it-works"
          >
            See how it works
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-soft p-8 shadow-soft">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-5">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
              Stories by topic
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold text-ink">
              Nonfiction, professional, and fiction stories
            </p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">
              From science and history to business, leadership, and career growth — pick topics that match your goals.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-5">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
              Tap to save
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold text-ink">
              Instant definitions and translations
            </p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">
              Tap any word to capture it, then build your personal list.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-5">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
              Adaptive practice
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold text-ink">
              A system that learns how you learn
            </p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">
              It tracks which words you struggle with and adjusts automatically — so you spend less time reviewing and remember more.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container pb-16">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">
          Product preview
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink">
          See the reading and practice flow.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <figure class="rounded-3xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-4 shadow-soft">
          <img
            src="/screenshots/step-1-categories.png"
            alt="Category selection showing Nonfiction, Professional, and Fiction topics"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
            <strong class="text-ink">Pick a topic</strong> — Choose from nonfiction, professional, or fiction stories.
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="rounded-3xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-4 shadow-soft">
          <img
            src="/screenshots/step-2-reading.png"
            alt="Reading view with word popup showing translation and example"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
            <strong class="text-ink">Read and tap</strong> — Tap words for instant translations and examples.
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="rounded-3xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-4 shadow-soft">
          <img
            src="/screenshots/step-3-practice.png"
            alt="Practice flashcard with spaced repetition buttons"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
            <strong class="text-ink">Smart review</strong> — The system adapts to your memory and schedules practice at the right time.
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-surface py-16">
      <div class="container grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Context over isolation</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
            Stories keep words anchored in meaning, so learning feels natural.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Personalized difficulty</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
            Choose your level from A1 to C1 and grow at your pace.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Lightweight practice</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
            Quick review sessions keep words fresh without draining focus.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Professional vocabulary</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
            Learn business, leadership, and career terms in context — perfect for work and interviews.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="how-it-works" class="container py-16">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink">How Readerly works</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
              Step 1
            </p>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Pick a topic</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">
              Browse nonfiction, professional, or fiction stories — from science and history to business and leadership.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
              Step 2
            </p>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Read & tap words</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">
              Tap words to see definitions, translations, and examples.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
              Step 3
            </p>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">
              Review that adapts to you
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">
              Our system learns which words stick and which need more attention. It schedules reviews at the perfect moment — right before you'd forget.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-surface py-16">
      <div class="container grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr]">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">
            FAQ
          </p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-ink">
            Quick answers before you start.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-5">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">
              Is Readerly good for beginners?
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
              Yes. You can choose a language level from A1 to C1 and learn at your
              pace.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-5">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">
              How do I save new words?
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
              Tap any word while reading to see its translation and add it to your
              vocabulary list.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-5">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">
              How does practice work?
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
              Our review system learns how you learn. It tracks which words come easily and which need more practice, then adjusts timing automatically. You spend less time reviewing and remember more.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-5">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base font-semibold text-ink">
              Do I need to set a daily schedule?
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
              No. Review cards appear when you are ready, and sessions stay quick.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container py-16">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">
          Social proof
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink">What learners love</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <figure class="rounded-3xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
            <blockquote class="text-base text-ink">
              "I used to stop every 2 minutes to look up words. Now I just tap and keep reading—finally finished my first English novel last month."
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
              — Maria from Madrid
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rounded-3xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
            <blockquote class="text-base text-ink">
              "The business stories helped me understand terms I kept hearing in meetings. My manager noticed I stopped asking what 'stakeholder alignment' means."
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
              — Kenji, product manager in Berlin
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rounded-3xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
            <blockquote class="text-base text-ink">
              "5 minutes on the train each morning. That's it. After 3 months I went from struggling with articles to comfortably reading The Economist. Didn't expect that."
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
              — Sophie from Lyon
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container pb-20">
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-emerald-950 px-8 py-12 text-white lg:px-12">
        <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr]">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">
              Built for focus, designed for momentum.
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-200">
              Readerly keeps the experience clean, fast, and story-driven so you
              can learn without distractions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center gap-4 lg:items-end">
            <a
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-950"
              href="https://app.readerly.ai"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
            >
              Open Readerly
            </a>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">
              App runs at <span class="font-semibold">app.readerly.ai</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-emerald-100 bg-white">
      <div class="container flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-4 py-8 text-sm text-muted sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
      <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Readerly</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a class="hover:text-ink" href="mailto:hello@readerly.ai">Contact</a>
        <span>Privacy available on request</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
